set_banish_handler -  This method sets the banish handler.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_banish_handler(string hand)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^handler%^RESET%^ - the banish handler

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/punishments/banishment.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the banish handler.  The banish handler will be called
with two methods, one is:
.EP
.SP 5 5
banish_person(string name, int days)
.EP
.SP 5 5
banish_person_suspend(string name)
.EP

